By docking into a website with metamask enabled amd your game wallet equipped

Wsllet is checked for mining pick or a predetermined set of requirements are met (token check), ex If mining pick is present in wallet, then:

By spending time on the website, you would be air dropped asteroid ore into your wallet based off the level of your mining pick/laser.

Ore can then be used as the basis to craft more advanced materials and items using PoV gateways

proof of time (PoT) - rewarded for time spent on website with token airdropped to wallet on a certain time interval
